item: We aim to invest in maintaining the current state
We willen investeren in het behoud van de huidige staat
Wir wollen in die Erhaltung des derzeitigen Zustands investieren

We willen investeren in het aanbrengen van veranderingen en het verbeteren van de huidige staat

We willen investeren in het voorkomen van negatieve veranderingen in de huidige staat
Wir wollen in die Verhinderung negativer Veränderungen des derzeitigen Zustands investieren

"By imposing higher taxes on the rich, we can redistribute wealth from the rich to the middle class."     "We should address the tax gap between the rich and the middle class by increasing taxes on the wealthy."     "By levying higher taxes on the rich, we can create a more equitable society where everyone pays their fair share."     "We can alleviate the financial strain on middle-class Americans by implementing progressive taxation policies."   ] }
extract: We can alleviate the financial strain on middle-class Americans by implementing progressive taxation policies.

item: We firmly reject any involvement with NATO and will resolutely oppose the use of Shannon Airport as a transit point for military operations.
paraphrase_0: {   "language": "English",   "paraphrases": [     "We firmly reject any involvement with NATO and will resolutely oppose the use of Shannon Airport as a transit point for military operations.",     "We stand firmly against any attempt by NATO to use Shannon Airport as a military base, and we will resolutely oppose any such attempt.",     "We categorically reject the use of Shannon Airport as a military base and will work tirelessly to ensure that it remains free from any such involvement.",     "We unequivocally denounce any suggestion that Shannon Airport be used for military purposes and will vehemently oppose any such attempt.",     "We resolutely oppose any and all efforts to establish Shannon Airport as a military base and will work towards ensuring that it remains a civilian airport."   ] }

item: The allocation of significant resources to public infrastructure represents a substantial commitment to the development and maintenance of essential facilities and services in Europe.

paraphrase_0: {   "language": "English",   "paragraph": "Our aims—the aims of this Republican crusade—are clear: to sweep from office an administration which has fastened on every one of us the wastefulness, the arrogance and corruption in high places, the heavy bur-dens and anxieties which are the bitter fruit of a party too long in power.",   "paraphrases": [     "Our primary objective is to remove an administration that has abused its authority and has fostered a culture of arrogance and corruption within our government.",     "We seek an administration that prioritizes transparency and accountability, free from the influence of special interests and special pleading.",     "Our mission is to restore faith in our political institutions and to create a government that is truly representative of all the people.",     "We demand an administration that is committed to addressing the concerns of ordinary citizens, rather than catering to the interests of wealthy donors and special interests.",     "Our ultimate goal is to create a more just and equitable society where everyone has the opportunity to succeed, regardless of their background or status."   ] }
extract: Our ultimate goal is to create a more just and equitable society where everyone has the opportunity to succeed, regardless of their background or status.

item: We aim to stimulate the economy by rehiring millions of people and subsequently ensuring that those unable to work earn enough to maintain a decent standard of living.
paraphrase_0: {   "language": "English",   "paraphrases": [     "We aim to stimulate the economy by rehiring millions of people and subsequently ensuring that those unable to work earn enough to maintain a decent standard of living." "By prioritizing the well-being of our citizens, we aim to create a more prosperous and equitable society for all."   ] }
